title: Glick Luxury Roll Wrap, Football Gift Wrapping Paper, 2 metres x 70 cms, Suitable for Birthdays and Other Occasions, Green
features: LUXURY BIRTHDAY WRAP: This premium wrapping paper adds a touch of luxury to birthday celebrations. Wrap all your gifts in our Glick Luxury Roll Wrap designed with a Football theme for those Footie mad fans.
EXTRAVAGANT: Make any birthday special with our Football Gift Wrapping Paper. The lively Football design brings an extra layer of excitement to presents, measuring 2 meters by 70 cm.

HIGH QUALITY AND ECO-FRIENDLY: Crafted from 80GSM paper, our wrapping wrap feels substantial and perfect for wrapping various gift sizes, all while supporting responsible forest management through FSC-certified materials.
EFFORTLESS WRAPPING FOR ALL GIFTS: Whether it's toys or other items, our Glick Luxury Roll Wrap makes the process hassle-free, ensuring a memorable and enjoyable gift-giving experience.

COMPLETE GIFTING SOLUTION: Our range includes high-quality printed gift wrap, tags, and more, all tailored to occasions. Specifically designed for birthdays and celebrations, this wrapping paper captures the essence of youth.
description: Dive into our collection of innovative, high-quality printed gift wrap, accompanied by gift tags, convenient gift bags, versatile roll wrap, tasteful ribbons, bows that add the perfect finishing touch and tissue papers for a touch of intrigue. With our thoughtfully curated selection, your gifts will be transformed into memories for any time of year or celebration.
